data.description: WOW! Are you looking for more space? Well here it is, look no further. This wonderfully spacious home has a full finished lower level teen/inlaw suite with full bath. Extras include large rooms and closets, vaulted master suite, oversized rooms, back deck and patio, separate formal dining room, marble fireplace and large level private lot with mature landscaping. All this and a great location within easy access to I-20 and Shopping. Hurry!
